A cyberpunk scene showing a glowing green terminal screen in a dark hacker's den, with streams of raw data packets visualized as neon-colored geometric shapes flowing through transparent tubes that bypass an elaborate security gate made of intricate circuit patterns. The security gate appears impressive but hollow, with data easily slipping through gaps and cracks. In the foreground, a mechanical hand manipulates the data streams like a puppeteer, redirecting them around the supposed barriers. The atmosphere is moody with deep purples and electric blues, reflections bouncing off wet surfaces, and holographic warning symbols flickering uselessly in the background. Rain streaks across a nearby window showing a distant cityscape of towering servers.
